snippet.title: Gravitas: Johnny Depp denies hitting ex-wife, alleges Amber Heard was violent
snippet.description:
Gravitas: Johnny Depp denies hitting ex-wife, alleges Amber Heard was violent

Pirates of the Caribbean star Johnny Depp has said that his former wife Amber Heard was violent, and would regularly abuse him. Depp was appearing at a London court for the hearing of libel case against a British Tabloid.

#Gravitas #JohnnyDeppHittingWife #JohnnyDepp
